---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import { Navigation } from "../components/shared";
import HeroSection from "../components/pages/home/hero_section/hero_section.astro";
import Footer from "../components/shared/footer/index.astro";
---

<Layout>
    <Navigation client:load />
    
    <div class="about-container">
      <!-- Header section -->
   <header class="about-header border-t border-b border-gray-600  md:text-6xl font-playfair-display text-center mb-1 uppercase text-neutral-950">
  <h1 class="about-title">SOBRE NOSOTROS</h1>
</header>

      <!-- Top section with collage -->
      <div class="collage-section">
        <div class="quote-box-top">
          <div class="quote-text-top   md:text-6xl font-playfair-display text-center mb-1 uppercase text-neutral-950 ">
            “SUEÑA<br />
             EXPLORA<br />
             DESCUBRE.“
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="image-box-primary">
          <img
            src="https://sincerelyjules.com/wp-content/themes/sincerely/assets/img/pages/sj_about_image_01.png"
            alt="Seaside photo"
            class="image-primary object-cover"
          />
        </div>

        <div class="intro-box">
          <div class="intro-text text-neutral-700 leading-relaxed mb-4 text-sm sm:text-base">
            HOLA <br>Somos Camino Valiente, una comunidad apasionada por descubrir los rincones más hermosos del mundo.
            Este espacio es nuestro diario de viajes donde compartimos experiencias únicas, consejos útiles,
            fotografías inspiradoras y rutas inolvidables. Aquí podrás conocer lugares mágicos, culturas fascinantes,
            y encontrar motivación para planear tu próxima aventura. Creemos que viajar no solo abre la mente,
            sino también el corazón. Nuestra misión es contagiarte esa chispa viajera y animarte a vivir la vida
            con una mochila de sueños y una cámara llena de recuerdos. ¡Bienvenido a bordo, este es tu punto de partida!
          </div>
          <div class="intro-signature text-neutral-700 leading-relaxed mb-4 text-sm sm:text-base ">
            Con pasion,<br />
            Camino Valiente
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="image-box-secondary">
          <img
            src="https://sincerelyjules.com/wp-content/themes/sincerely/assets/img/pages/sj_about_image_02.png"
            alt="Black and white photo"
            class="image-secondary object-cover object-center"
          />
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Story section -->
      <div class="story-section flex flex-wrap"> 
        <div class="story-text text-neutral-700 leading-relaxed mb-4 text-sm sm:text-base">
          <p class="story-paragraph">
            I launched my blog in 2009 while attending FIDM where I studied
            Visual Communications. At the time, I was also interning at VSGN,
            assisting a few celebrity stylists, working a 9-5, and attending
            college. It was a lot! I remember starting to feel overwhelmed with
            everything on my plate and felt like I wasn't being as creative as I
            wanted to be.
          </p>
          <p class="story-paragraph">
            My sister suggested I start a fashion blog to help me fulfill this
            void, so I went for it! I had no idea what I was doing but figured
            it out as I went. It was hard to juggle everything all at once but
            the blog gave me a sense of peace and freedom that I didn't get with
            anything else so it kept me going. Being able to have my blog as a
            creative outlet helped me stay inspired and grow creatively.
          </p>
          <p class="story-paragraph">
            Now 12 years & over 5.7M+ followers later, I'm so humbled to have
            this little blog here because it changed my life forever. This blog
            will forever hold a special place in my heart! Since the beginning
            of SJ, I've always stayed true to myself and do things I genuinely
            love and believe in, but most importantly, I always follow my heart
            no matter what.
          </p>
          <p class="story-paragraph">
            If there's one thing I'd love for you to take away from visiting my
            blog is that YOU CAN DO ANYTHING you set your mind to! Believe in
            yourself and never give up even if it feels unreachable, trust the
            process and be patient and you'll see results! As I always say
            DREAM, BELIEVE, ACHIEVE!
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="image-box-tertiary">
          <img
            src="https://sincerelyjules.com/wp-content/themes/sincerely/assets/img/pages/sj_about_image_03.png"
            alt="Jules on beach"
            class="image-tertiary"
          />
        </div>

        <div class="quote-section-bottom relative w-full"> 
          <img
            src="https://sincerelyjules.com/wp-content/themes/sincerely/assets/img/pages/sj_about_image_04.png"
            alt="Jules in a field"
            class="image-quaternary block"
          />
          <div class="quote-box-bottom text-2xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl font-playfair-display text-center mb-1 uppercase text-neutral-950">
            "CUANDO VIAJAS <br />NO ES TRABAJO <br />ES PASION."
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
<style>

.about-container {
  @apply w-full relative;
  padding-left: 7%;
  padding-top: 5%;
}

.about-header {
  @apply pt-4 pb-4 border-b border-gray-200 mb-8;
}

.about-title {
  @apply text-center font-serif text-3xl tracking-wider font-normal;
  margin-right: 8%;
}

.collage-section {
  @apply relative h-auto mb-12; 
}

.quote-box-top {
  @apply absolute z-10;
  width: 35%;
  top: 5%;
  left: 0;
}

.quote-text-top {
  @apply  text-left;
  margin-left: 3rem;
}

.image-box-primary {
  @apply absolute right-0 top-0 overflow-hidden z-[1];
  width: 72%;
  height: auto; 
}

.image-primary {
  @apply w-full h-full;
}

.intro-box {
  @apply absolute z-10;
  width: 45%;
  right: 2%;
  bottom: 10%;
  margin-right: 10%;
}


.intro-text {
  @apply mb-4;
  font-size: 15px;
  line-height: 1.75;
}

.intro-signature {
  @apply mt-5;
  font-size: 0.75rem;
}

.image-box-secondary {
  @apply relative left-0 bottom-0 z-[2] overflow-hidden;
  width: 37%;
  height: auto; 
  padding-top: 25%;
}

.image-secondary {
  @apply w-full h-auto; 
}

.story-section {
  @apply relative pb-24;
}

.story-text {
  @apply w-1/2;
  margin-top: 6%;
  padding-left: 10%;
}

.story-paragraph {
  @apply mb-5;
}

.image-box-tertiary {
  @apply mb-12;
  width: 35%;
  margin-left: 15%;
}

.image-tertiary {
  width: 100%;
  height: 110%;
}

.image-quaternary {
  @apply h-auto;
  width: 50%;
  margin-left: 0;
  margin-right: 12%;
}

.quote-box-bottom {
  @apply absolute text-right z-[2];
  right: 10%;
  top: 50%;
  line-height: 1.2;
  margin-right: 25%;
}



/* Estilos para teléfonos móviles (hasta 768px) */
@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .about-container {
    @apply px-[5%]; 
    padding-left: 5%;
    padding-right: 5%;
    padding-top: 5%; 
  }

  .about-header {
    @apply mb-16;
  }

  .about-title {
    @apply text-lg text-left;
    margin-right: 0;
  }

  .collage-section {
    @apply static mb-8 flex flex-col items-center; 
      position: relative; 
  }

  .quote-box-top {
    @apply static w-[90%] mb-4 text-center; 
     position: absolute; 
     top: 7%; 
  left: 50%; 
  transform: translate(-50%, -50%); 
  z-index: 10; 
  text-align: center; 
   
  }

  .quote-text-top {
    @apply text-2xl ml-0;
  }

  .image-box-primary {
    @apply static w-full h-auto;

  }

  .image-primary {
    @apply ml-auto mr-0; 
    width: 72%; 
    height: auto;
  }

  .intro-box {
    @apply static w-[80%] ; 
    padding-top: 50px
  }

  .intro-text {
    @apply text-sm;
    text-align: left
  }

  .intro-signature {
   padding-bottom: 30px;
  }

  .image-box-secondary {
    @apply static w-full pt-0; 
    
  }

  .story-section {
    @apply static pb-8 flex flex-col ;
    margin-left: -10%
  }

  .story-text {
    @apply w-full mt-0 ;
    text-align: left;

  }

  .image-box-tertiary {
    @apply static w-full mb-8 ml-0; 
  }

  .image-tertiary {
    @apply ml-auto mr-0 ; 
    width: 70%; 
    height: auto; 
  }

  .quote-section-bottom {
    @apply static flex flex-col items-center w-full; 
  }

  .image-quaternary {
    @apply w-[90%] ml-0; 
    margin-right: 10px; 
  }

  .quote-box-bottom {
    @apply static w-[90%] mt-4 text-center mr-0; 
  }
}

/*  ESTILOS PARA 769px - 1465px  */
@media (min-width: 769px) and (max-width: 1465px) {
  .about-container {
    padding-left: 5%; 
    padding-right: 5%; 
    padding-top: 4%;
  }

  .about-title {
    @apply text-2xl text-center; 
    margin-right: 0; 
  }


  .collage-section {
    @apply static flex flex-col items-center gap-8 mb-10; 
  }

  .quote-box-top {
    @apply static w-full max-w-2xl text-center; 
    order: 1; 
  }

  .quote-text-top {
    @apply text-4xl; 
    margin-left: 0; 
  }

  .image-box-primary {
    @apply static w-full max-w-3xl mx-auto; 
    order: 2;
  }

  .intro-box {
    @apply static w-full max-w-2xl mx-auto text-left; 
    margin-right: 0;
    padding: 1rem; 
    order: 3;
  }

  .intro-text {
    @apply text-base;
  }

  .intro-signature {
    @apply text-center mt-4;
  }

  .image-box-secondary {
    @apply static w-full max-w-xl mx-auto pt-0;
    order: 4;
  }

  .story-section {
    @apply static flex flex-col items-center gap-8 pb-16; 
  }

  .story-text {
    @apply w-full max-w-3xl text-left; 
    margin-top: 0;
    padding-left: 0;
  }

  .story-paragraph {
    @apply text-base;
  }

  .image-box-tertiary {
    @apply w-full max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-8; 
    margin-left: 0;
  }

  .image-tertiary {
    height: auto; 
  }

  .quote-section-bottom {
    @apply static flex flex-col items-center gap-4 w-full;
  }

  .image-quaternary {
    @apply w-full max-w-2xl mx-auto; 
    margin-right: 0;
  }

  .quote-box-bottom {
    @apply static w-full max-w-xl text-center text-2xl;
    margin-right: 0;
    top: auto; right: auto; 
  }
}
</style>  
    <Footer />
</Layout>